{"tid":2478360,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"中國新華網放風，即將整治動畫產業","createTime":"2021-04-07T04:09:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T06:28:08.000Z","uid":64191,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"f416d872aab5e7f1cb92b543d22ef331740121af","tid":2478360,"uid":64191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T04:09:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/jCvyeiF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FjCvyeiF.png&h=dfd33482&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國官媒新華網做左個調查，顯示八成家長同意加強控管動畫尺度，理由是過於血腥暴力，仲特別點名《超人迪加》及熊出沒<br />\n<br />\n消息一出，群情洶湧。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/qQWIAZq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FqQWIAZq.png&h=57fef9c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/wBPsuyW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FwBPsuyW.png&h=fdd17580&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/fkh3o5L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Ffkh3o5L.png&h=df117cdd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n留言截錄<br />\n<br />\n「持械毆打？西遊記都係喎，講迪加？」<br />\n<br />\n「要放風進口動畫先審後播？」<br />\n<br />\n「我細個都睇迪加啦，而家啲細路唔睇得？」<br />\n<br />\n「持械毆打、多人恐嚇、縱火爆炸？建議禁埋《戰狼》」<br />\n<br />\n「管唔掂細路仔，搵藉口？」"},{"pid":"e625e88dce13d9d22cf5ac7c13cada20bd98ad09","tid":2478360,"uid":192517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T04:11:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e220483997a876d0d4fb5d08f734e5cae30bb6e6","tid":2478360,"uid":180124,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T04:13:48.000Z","msg":"超人唔係奶共既咩？"},{"pid":"af82bd96c9dbafcc5473e4c7aed6043625b70713","tid":2478360,"uid":44646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e